title: Search and rescue efforts delay Ferry Puyallup
text:
The Coast Guard is helping search for a possible man overboard on the Seattle-Bainbridge Island ferry run.
Wednesday afternoon's search impacts sailings for Ferry Puyallup.
The 6:20 p.m. sailing from Seattle to Bainbridge Island will be delayed. The 5:30 p.m. sailing from Bainbridge was also affected.
Stay with kiro7.com for updates.
